{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/en/joomla-hilfe/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Self-explanatory software is ideal. But which programme is? For this reason, help is always a useful addition. Depending on the system, help pages cannot be found immediately or are even hidden. Joomla offers a uniform procedure for this.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/afea42d680cad283a14f53aa27ac604c/191e2/j4x27x1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.10126582278481%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Joomla Help link in the list view\"\n        title=\"Joomla Help link in the list view\"\n        src=\"/static/afea42d680cad283a14f53aa27ac604c/f058b/j4x27x1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/afea42d680cad283a14f53aa27ac604c/c26ae/j4x27x1.png 158w,\n/static/afea42d680cad283a14f53aa27ac604c/6bdcf/j4x27x1.png 315w,\n/static/afea42d680cad283a14f53aa27ac604c/f058b/j4x27x1.png 630w,\n/static/afea42d680cad283a14f53aa27ac604c/40601/j4x27x1.png 945w,\n/static/afea42d680cad283a14f53aa27ac604c/78612/j4x27x1.png 1260w,\n/static/afea42d680cad283a14f53aa27ac604c/191e2/j4x27x1.png 1836w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>For impatient people</h2>\n<p>Look at the changed programme code in the <a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t22...t23\">Diff View</a> and incorporate these changes into your development version.</p>\n<h2>Step by step</h2>\n<h3>New files</h3>\n<p>In this chapter, only files are changed.</p>\n<h3>Modified files</h3>\n<p>Two lines per view are sufficient to display a button at the top right that contains a question mark as an icon and has an Internet address specified in the code as the link target. I have chosen <code class=\"language-text\">http://joomla.org</code> as an example. The principle is clear. You have the possibility to create a separate help file for each <code class=\"language-text\">View</code> and to link it in the view of the component - exactly where questions usually arise.</p>\n<h4><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t22...t23#diff-d25fe4d29c25ccf10e0ba6ecaf837294\">administrator/components/com_foos/ src/View/Foo/HtmlView.php</a></h4>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container grvsc-has-line-highlighting solarized-light\" data-language=\"php\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">ToolbarHelper::</span><span class=\"mtk7\">divider</span><span class=\"mtk1\">();</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">ToolbarHelper::</span><span class=\"mtk7\">help</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&#39;&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk5\">false</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&#39;http://joomla.org&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span></code></pre>\n<h4><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t22...t23#diff-8e3d37bbd99544f976bf8fd323eb5250\">administrator/components/com_foos/ src/View/Foos/HtmlView.php</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/blob/af04f8493aa045e8bcb2a49b8b1f8a60a927d78a/src/administrator/components/com_foos/src/View/Foos/HtmlView.php\">administrator/components/com_foos/ src/View/Foos/HtmlView.php</a></p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container grvsc-has-line-highlighting solarized-light\" data-language=\"php\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">ToolbarHelper::</span><span class=\"mtk7\">divider</span><span class=\"mtk1\">();</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">ToolbarHelper::</span><span class=\"mtk7\">help</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&#39;&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk5\">false</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&#39;http://joomla.org&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2>Test your Joomla component</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>install your component in Joomla version 4 to test it:</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Copy the files in the <code class=\"language-text\">administrator</code> folder into the <code class=\"language-text\">administrator</code> folder of your Joomla 4 installation.</p>\n<p>A new installation is not necessary. Continue using the files from the previous part.</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Open the view of your component in the administration area. Click on the help link and make sure that you are redirected to the help page you entered.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e25bb038ed65387e503b853b6fad3d01/191e2/j4x27x2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.10126582278481%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Joomla Help Link in the item view\"\n        title=\"Joomla Help Link in the item view\"\n        src=\"/static/e25bb038ed65387e503b853b6fad3d01/f058b/j4x27x2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e25bb038ed65387e503b853b6fad3d01/c26ae/j4x27x2.png 158w,\n/static/e25bb038ed65387e503b853b6fad3d01/6bdcf/j4x27x2.png 315w,\n/static/e25bb038ed65387e503b853b6fad3d01/f058b/j4x27x2.png 630w,\n/static/e25bb038ed65387e503b853b6fad3d01/40601/j4x27x2.png 945w,\n/static/e25bb038ed65387e503b853b6fad3d01/78612/j4x27x2.png 1260w,\n/static/e25bb038ed65387e503b853b6fad3d01/191e2/j4x27x2.png 1836w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:mid